<HEADLINE> Sen. Edward Kennedy Hospitalized  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON (AP) -- Sen. Edward Kennedy, D-Mass., is undergoing observation at
a Washington hospital for a viral illness that his spokesman said caused back
and shoulder pain.
</P>
