    NEW YORK (AP) -- Stock prices have opened mostly lower and the Dow Jones
industrial average is down 24 points in today's early going. Losing issues on
the New York Stock Exchange hold a slim lead over gainers. The Nasdaq composite
index is ahead 30 points and the Standard &AMP; Poor's 500 stock index is down a
point.
</P>
<P>
	   The market won't have much to go on today. Companies reporting earnings are
few and far between.
