<TEXT>
<P>
    NEW YORK (AP) -- Stocks that are moving substantially or trading heavily
today on the New York Stock Exchange and Nasdaq Stock Market.
</P>
<P>
	   The defense contractor said it expects to post second-quarter earnings of 80
cents per share. Analysts had expected Litton to earn $1.05 a share. Litton
cited costs for two development programs in its advanced electronics segment.
</P>
<P>
	   Gold prices have surged in recent days after Placer Dome, one of the world's
leading gold producers, said it will stop selling borrowed gold as a hedge
against lower prices. Other gold producers are believed to be considering
similar strategies.
</P>
