Seabrooks was arrested last fall for fighting and pleaded guilty to harassment
and disorderly conduct, receiving a 90-day suspended sentence.
</P>
<P>
	   Freshman Donatas Zavackas was benched for two games this season for
undisclosed reasons.
</P>
<P>
	   And last year, Pitt was embarrassed when former player Fred Primus was
arrested on theft charges during a road trip to Villanova.
</P>
